graph TD
    start[Start] --> check_stairs[Check all :pink[Stair] objects]
    check_stairs --> loop{For each :pink[Stair]}
    loop --> check_compartments[Check if :pink[Stair] connects multiple :pink[Compartment]s]
    check_compartments --> is_connecting{Does it connect<br>multiple compartments?}
    is_connecting -->|Yes| check_enclosed[Check if :pink[Stair] is enclosed]
    is_connecting -->|No| next_stair[Next :pink[Stair]]
    next_stair --> loop
    check_enclosed --> is_enclosed{Is :pink[Stair] enclosed?}
    is_enclosed -->|Yes| apply_principles[Apply principles from<br>Section 2 "Compartimentering<br>en evacuatie"]
    is_enclosed -->|No| fail[Fail: :pink[Stair] connecting<br>multiple compartments<br>must be enclosed]
    apply_principles --> next_stair
    fail --> next_stair
    loop -->|No more stairs| end[End]

style start fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
style end fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
style fail fill:#f99,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px